      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIN ROOF RUSTY (1) boasts a strong record this journey with nine wins and seven minors from 19 tries. Was out of placings last time (26.65) at this track in a NG, finishing seventh and beaten 16 lengths. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. IRINKA ALANA (2) clocked a fast 19.76 when placed over 350m at Goulburn last start in a Grade 5. Harder here but expected to measure up. ELITE DOM (4) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten 1.75 lengths, (30.46) at Wagga. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Likely to be in the finish again. MY THREE BOYS (5) is always hard to beat when he races here at this trip.",
